:: Aidan_sister {"position":"850,1850","size":"100,100"}
His brow furrows and his jaw tightens as he recounts his family's history. He soon collects himself and states that he has an older sister and a younger sister. He said his older sister named Eliza was trained to be the next duchess since in the Rokian Empire it was not unheard of that an only daughter or eldest daughter would take the title. He continues, explaining that his younger sister Roza excels in combat and leadership. The prince thinks for a moment and states that Eliza may have deposed him as she sees the duchy of Diamond Bay as her birthright, while Roza assisted to gain personal glory as she was shunned constantly by their parents. Turning to you, he states that whatever the case may be or their reasons it was still unjust of them to depose him. He soon looked towards the eastern window and remarked that he was going to abdicate the duchy to Eliza in six months time anyway since he believes he couldn't be a good duke.

Looking at the prince you decide too ask...

[[Why Hoxea is more diverse and more tolerant than other nations|Aidan_Hoxea]]
